{"type":null,"faqId":46093,"title":"为什么灭屏后WLAN下载停止？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:0.5416667in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>请确认您是否修改过“在休眠状态下保持WLAN连接”，默认该选项是“始终”，即灭屏不影响下载；若该选项选择的是“限充电时”或“从不”，则灭屏后WLAN会断开连接，下载会停止：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1、点击WLAN高级设置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=170737\" style=\"width:2.3069444in;height:4.1041665in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>2、然后在高级设置页面点击“在休眠状态下保持WLAN连接”，选择点击“始终”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=170738\" style=\"width:2.2625in;height:4.0201387in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1873","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1444376107000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":18,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"灭屏,休眠,黑屏,下载,无线网络,中断,停止","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}